'''Iriaebor''' ({{Pronounce|eer|ee|AY|bore|refs=}}), also known as the '''Overland City''' and the '''City of a Thousand Spires''', was a large city in [[Sunset Vale]] in the [[Western Heartlands]] region of [[west Faerûn]]. While it retained its status as an independent city-state, it remained within the realm of influence of the 15{{th}} century nation of [[Elturgard]].

While it was considered to be one of the most densely-populated and economically influential locales in [[West Faerûn|western Faerûn]], it was believed its true potential as a great power was stymied by the petty squabbles and in-fighting that plagued many of its residents.

{{Quote|Iriaebor is like [[Waterdeep]] gone mad when it comes to merchant manipulations, chicanery, and maneuvering.|[[Volothamp Geddarm]], from his [[Volo's Guide to the Sword Coast (in-universe)|namesake guide to the Sword Coast]].}}
